{"id":"5101c47e-0c68-4b6a-9609-53251a492874","name":"Shizune Inari","description":"<p>She was bored and decided to blow up your planet for a bit of fun. Surprisingly you survived, but you probably wish you had gone with the rest of your world.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(197, 76, 76);\"><strong>You know? I've never had a chance to study a survivor of a planet I've destroyed before. I do hope you prove entertaining.</strong></span></p><p>Art by <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/Saex250\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>SaijaxW</em></strong></a></p><p>Shizune Inari belongs to<strong><em> </em></strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/HeavenlySize\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Heavenlysize</em></strong></a></p><p><em>Art below by</em><strong><em> </em></strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/Lajest3D\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Lajest3D</em></strong></a></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6qWwMPsymiOwKHm7Fy3bR.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/d9eqhyNMeggcI3F2lJhfZ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(197, 76, 76);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(197, 76, 76); color: inherit;\">Giantess growth, Lajest, evie, darcey, kitsune, fox</mark></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"PqMpdFi0u7WSKMtVBVYuh.webp","creator":"TMNT94","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🔮 Magical","👽 Alien","🧖 Giant","⛓️ Dominant","🧬 Demi-Human","👨 MalePov","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":2470,"messages":52833,"created_at":"2025-03-10T23:30:09.808796+00:00"}